s. I especially dig how you let me mix and match three tacos, so I can add a red chili pork taco and fried fish taco into the mix!  Your cute little bistro setting with the beaded lamps and cushy bench seating made a delightful setting for a first date, while your exemplary menu, service and specials has had me coming back ever since. It's a good thing I'm not the jealous type, because I want to share you with all of Tempe.

